comments: Edwards (MIN) legally contests the perimeter shot attempt by Morant (MEM).
Jones (MEM) legally contests the shot attempt by McDaniels (MIN).

Jones (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of McLaughlin (MIN) and marginal contact occurs as the latter fights through the pick.  Edwards (MIN) initiates marginal contact with Jones that does not dislodge him from his position.
McLaughlin (MIN) legally contests Jones' (MEM) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.

Edwards (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Morant (MEM) and the former's right arm comes out and brushes the front of Morant, who is able to play on through the marginal touch.
Morant (MEM) legally contests the driving shot attempt by McLaughlin (MIN).
McLaughlin (MIN) reaches in to make a play on the pass and marginal body contact occurs with Jackson Jr. (MEM), who is able to maintain control of the ball.
Towns (MIN) raises his right arm up and it grazes the right arm of Jackson Jr. (MEM) during the dunk attempt at the rim and the contact is marginal.
Beverley (MIN) gathers the ball and takes three steps before releasing his shot attempt.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Towns (MIN) reaches his arm up for the ball and is the last to make contact with it before it falls out of bounds. Possession is correctly awarded to Memphis.
Beverley (MIN) commits a take foul on Morant (MEM).
McLaughlin (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Clarke (MEM) and marginal contact occurs to the latter's chest as the former firms up.
McDaniels (MIN) establishes himself in a wide screening position in the path of Bane (MEM) and marginal leg contact occurs as Bane moves over the screen.
Clarke (MEM) legally contests the perimeter shot attempt from Edwards (MIN).
Beverley (MIN) commits a take foul on Jackson Jr. (MEM).
Jackson Jr. (MEM) retreats backwards as he absorbs the marginal contact initiated by Edwards (MIN) during the driving shot attempt.
McLaughlin's (MIN) arms are to the side of Bane (MEM) and he slides them off as Bane cuts towards the baseline and the contact is marginal. Bane loses his balance and falls to the floor.
Edwards (MIN) briefly grasps Morant's (MEM) right arm before deflecting the ball out of bounds.
Edwards (MIN) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Edwards (MIN) reaches in and commits a take foul on Morant (MEM).
